item.title: [Delta]Making interface go fullscreen? [Delta] Will rep++ who helps me
item.description:
@411 wrote:

I’m trying to add the login interface to my delta based server, i have it added but i cant figure out how to make it go full screen. I also couldnt find any tutorials on it.

This is the code:
getTotalLevel();
specAttack();
l33thax(12323);
l33thax(7574);
l33thax(7599);
l33thax(7549);
l33thax(8493);
l33thax(7499);
sM(“Welcome to Server.”);
checkDupe();
sendQuestSomething(15244);
showInterface(15244);

So whenever someone logs in it shows the login interface, which is 15244, but it wont go fullscreen. It does this:

I’m absolutly clueless on how to make it go fullscreen. Like i said, i cant find any tutorials on it, and i cant figure it out myself. If someone can tell me how to make the login interface go fullscreen, ill rep++ you. Thanks.
